                                          ALEXIS Array of Low Energy X-Ray Imaging Sensors

                               ALEXIS is a mini-satellite containing six wide
                                   angle EUV/ultrasoft X-ray telescopes and a
                                   broad-band VHF receiver and digitizer,
                                   BLACKBEARD.


